Open,Assessments,is,a,service,for,creating,and,sharing,questions,in,order,to,assess,people,s,knowledge,Questions,created,through,Open,Assessments,can,be,embedded,on,any,page,of,any,website,Users,can,create,and,retrieve,assessments,programmatically,via,REST,API,This,service,was,built,by,Open,Tapestry,with,funding,from,MIT